  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562800/extras/b31672bb507955b3100aa0b5a75951a9.avif?t=1768868609\" width=600 height=160 /></span><br><br>As a photographer, you can start with the model's hairstyle, makeup and clothing, and create unique works with various props.<br><br>As a photographer, you can fight for money by fulfilling the requirements of customers, so as to unlock more clothes and props.<br><br>As a photographer, you can cultivate your own model and play with her.<br><br>As a photographer, play with you<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562800/extras/6530f56870940b0912b05c028447518e.poster.avif?t=1768868609\" width=710 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562800/extras/6530f56870940b0912b05c028447518e.webm?t=1768868609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562800/extras/6530f56870940b0912b05c028447518e.mp4?t=1768868609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Main contents:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Set up the studio in the first person<br></li><li>Choose hairstyle, make-up and clothes for models<br></li><li>Choose the body posture, gesture and expression of the model. Adjust the pose of the model from the first perspective<br></li><li> Free camera perspective<br></li><li>Rich shooting props that can be unlocked</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562800/extras/563c085d0c9cf336912e166db5122110.poster.avif?t=1768868609\" width=730 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562800/extras/563c085d0c9cf336912e166db5122110.webm?t=1768868609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562800/extras/563c085d0c9cf336912e166db5122110.mp4?t=1768868609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
